medium article link:
https://mrprabhatmishra.medium.com/periodic-email-scheduler-in-django-with-celery-beat-72c5b4d0b9d

github repository
https://github.com/prabhatmishra1/Scheduling-emails-with-celery/tree/master

Start celery in new terminal:
celery -A <project name> worker --pool=solo -l info


Start celery beat in new terminal
celery -A <project name> beat -l INFO


Run the below command if you want to kill the workers
celery -A main purge


